# CQ Signal local environment.
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in values. Pick Option A OR Option B.

# Option A: Vercel AI Gateway (recommended for production and preview deploys).
# - Get an API key at https://vercel.com/dashboard/ai-gateway
# - When deployed to a linked Vercel project, OIDC auth kicks in automatically
#   and this key is not needed.
# - Benefits: provider failover, cost tracking, observability.
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=

# Option B: Direct Anthropic API key (fastest for local dev with no Vercel link).
# - Get one at https://console.anthropic.com
# - NOTE: This is separate from Claude Max / Claude Code. Max covers claude.ai
#   and Claude Code usage. Programmatic API calls need this key with billing.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
